A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a sleek silver Mac Mini computer sitting on a warm wooden desk, with a small friendly robot assistant emerging from behind it, offering a golden key on a velvet cushion. The scene is bathed in soft amber afternoon light streaming through a window with lace curtains. In the background, a cozy home office setting with potted plants and family photos in frames. The robot has an earnest, helpful expression with rosy cheeks. Muted retro color palette of creams, teals, and warm oranges, with subtle halftone texture throughout giving it a nostalgic magazine advertisement feel.
